ed="T" n="0800b14"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0800b14"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000057512"><placeName>常州</placeName><placeName>興寧寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010863">義宣</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0800b15"/><persName key="A010863">釋義宣</persName>者，<placeName key="PL000000009723">晉陵</placeName>人也。<anchor xml:id="beg0800004"/>宿植<anchor xml:id="end0800004"/>利根，翛然<ptr type="glossary" target="#g501"/>出俗，<lb
ed="T" n="0800b16"/>不煩師訓，砥礪厥心。納法後，孜孜律科，時<lb
ed="T" n="0800b17"/>無虛度。玄儒旁綜，長在篇章，卒問<ptr type="glossary" target="#g519"/>捷給<ptr type="glossary" target="#g520"/>。而<lb
ed="T" n="0800b18"/>稟<ref type="person" target="#A019341">延陵</ref>恭讓之風，雅得毘尼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g900"/>之體。初<placeName key="PL000000010783"><anchor xml:id="beg0800sgsz3"/>揚<anchor xml:id="end0800sgsz3"/>州</placeName><persName key="A009590">法<lb
ed="T" n="0800b19"/>慎</persName>傳<anchor xml:id="begd1e25138"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e25138"/>舊章<ptr target="#n903"/>，<placeName key="PL000000000195">淮甸</placeName>之間，推為碩匠。<date notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14" key="j19921141993438" notAfter-iso="+0745-09-30"><name>天寶</name>初</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0800b20"/><persName key="A010863">宣</persName>斂衽<ptr type="glossary" target="#g521"/>摳衣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g517"/>，諮詢彌久，輩流<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g630"/>率服。<persName key="A009590">慎</persName>且歎<lb
ed="T" n="0800b21"/>賞曰：「可畏乎！」<persName key="A010863">宣</persName>講<persName key="A001519">終南</persName>《事鈔》<ptr target="#n1290"/>，請業于<persName key="A011002">周<roleName>律<lb
ed="T" n="0800b22"/>師</roleName></persName>之庭，考覈尤精，乃著《折中記》六卷以解<lb
ed="T" n="0800b23"/>之。蓋慊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g710"/><persName key="A010829">融濟</persName>、<persName key="A010823">㠋</persName>、<persName key="A010930">勝</persName>諸師有所紕謬故也。<lb
ed="T" n="0800b24"/>使是非各盡其分，人免據宗而阿比<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1354"/>，從此<lb
ed="T" n="0800b25"/>立稱<ptr type="glossary" target="#g523"/>耳。<placeName key="PL000000009739">毘陵</placeName>多出名士僧，有<persName key="G000024">三宣</persName>，<persName key="A011003">慧</persName>、<persName key="A009173">德</persName>、<persName key="A010863">義</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0800b26"/>是歟。時於<placeName key="PL000000010789">江都</placeName>習業，與<placeName key="PL000000013239">會稽</placeName><persName key="A004177">曇一</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000017104">閩川</placeName><persName key="A010861">懷<lb
ed="T" n="0800b27"/>一</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000011901">慶雲</placeName><persName key="A009591">靈一</persName>同門為朋也。<placeName key="PL000000009723">晉陵</placeName>既有<persName key="G000024">三宣</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0800b28"/><persName key="A009590">慎</persName>門復出<persName key="G000102">三一</persName>焉。<placeName key="PL000000000197">江表</placeName>資為美談。<persName key="A010863">宣</persName><date notBefore-iso="+0752-12-30" key="j19960861997410" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-15"><name>天寶</name>末</date><lb
ed="T" n="0800b29"/>盛行化導，罔究其終。</p><pb ed="T" n="0800c" xml:id="T50.2061.0800c"/>
    <p xml:id="pT50p0800c0101"><lb
ed="T" n="0800c01"/>系曰：夫名以制義，所出無窮，奈何師資<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1172"/>踵<lb
ed="T" n="0800c02"/>武<ptr type="glossary" target="#g526"/>，而犯教祖之諱乎？通曰：「《春秋》貴賤不嫌<lb
ed="T" n="0800c03"/>同號也<ptr target="#n1259"/>。」或曰：「<name>滕</name>、<name>齊</name>不敵<ptr type="glossary" target="#g527"/>，俱書『侯』，乃曰『不<lb
ed="T" n="0800c04"/>嫌同號』。號與名豈得例諸？」通曰：「號大不<lb
ed="T" n="0800c05"/>嫌，名小豈嫌乎？矧<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g325"/>以<persName key="A010863">義宣</persName>始為名者，安知<lb
ed="T" n="0800c06"/>弟子成事於<persName key="A001519">南山</persName>之門邪？然出家者必也無<lb
ed="T" n="0800c07"/>妨。一則姓既以<name>華</name>從<name>梵</name>，咸稱<name>釋</name>氏。一則<placeName key="PL000000055436">西<lb
ed="T" n="0800c08"/>域</placeName>無諱，此合從旃<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1050"/>。<anchor xml:id="beg0800005"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>具</sic><corr>且</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0800005"/>諱者<placeName key="PL000000042030">周</placeName>人以事鬼<lb
ed="T" n="0800c09"/>神，<placeName key="PL000000023563">夏</placeName><placeName key="PL000000000095">商</placeName>無諱明矣。況乎<persName key="A010863">宣<roleName>師</roleName></persName>已生<placeName key="PL000000055446">兜率</placeName>，小<lb
ed="T" n="0800c10"/>為天人，大為菩薩，豈宜以鬼神事之？致<lb
ed="T" n="0800c11"/>令<date notBefore-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469511973336" notAfter-iso="+0690-09-16"><name>唐</name>初</date>高德勝士，往往止存一字名，職由諱<lb
ed="T" n="0800c12"/>之極矣。屬今修撰，乃闕文也。乃知真諦無<lb
ed="T" n="0800c13"/>諱，俗諦聞似則懼。」或曰：「今沙門姓既為<name>釋</name>，<lb
ed="T" n="0800c14"/>名復不諱，言我不隨俗諦，云何對君主稱<lb
ed="T" n="0800c15"/>臣？莫<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>有否？」通曰：「姓名不對王者，臣<lb
ed="T" n="0800c16"/>妾表疏合然。昔<persName key="A003032">齊帝</persName>問<persName key="A003052">王儉</persName>，遂令對見稱<lb
ed="T" n="0800c17"/>名，自<date notBefore-iso="+0023-03-09" key="j17295281997410" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-15"><name>漢</name>至<name>唐</name></date>。<persName key="A004378">肅宗</persName>朝始見稱臣<ptr target="#n1262"/>，由此沿<lb
ed="T" n="0800c18"/>而不革。良以沙門德薄，日就衰微，一往無<lb
ed="T" n="0800c19"/>復矣。又以法委<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1556"/>國王，誠難改作。王謂為是，<lb
ed="T" n="0800c20"/>楷定莫移。故<persName key="A002799">佛</persName>言『雖非我制，諸方為清淨<lb
ed="T" n="0800c21"/>者，不得不行也。』<ptr target="#n1263"/>」</p>
